  "title": "* Sales Performance Executive – Training Provided",
  "description": "<p><strong>Sales Performance Executive – Training Provided</strong><br /><strong>Commission-Based | Face-to-Face Sales | Full Training Provided</strong></p><p>A commission-based role with structured training, mentorship, and personal development. Strong performers will progress into leadership and management.</p><p>This is a <strong>hands-on, people-facing sales role</strong>, designed for individuals who want real-world experience, measurable results, and fast career growth. You’ll work on the ground, engaging customers directly and representing client brands through performance-driven sales campaigns.</p><p>This role is <strong>not</strong> a desk job, not digital marketing, and not behind-the-scenes work.</p><h3><strong>What You’ll Be Doing</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Execute <strong>face-to-face sales and marketing campaigns</strong></p></li><li><p>Engage customers directly to represent client brands</p></li><li><p>Drive sales results and track daily performance</p></li><li><p>Learn sales psychology, communication, and closing skills</p></li><li><p>Develop leadership capabilities through hands-on execution</p></li><li><p>Progress into team leadership and management roles based on performance</p></li></ul><h3><strong>What We Provide</strong></h3><p>📚 Structured sales training (no experience required)<br />🎯 Ongoing mentorship and coaching<br />💰 <strong>Commission-based earnings with uncapped potential</strong><br />📈 Clear, merit-based career progression<br />🌱 Personal development in confidence, communication, and leadership<br />🔥 Young, driven, and high-energy team environment</p><h3><strong>Who This Role Is For</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Fresh graduates & ORD personnel</p></li><li><p>Career switchers seeking skill-based growth</p></li><li><p>Individuals ready to step out of their comfort zone</p></li><li><p>Self-motivated, goal-oriented personalities</p></li><li><p>People who enjoy face-to-face interaction and measurable results</p></li></ul><p>⚠️ <strong>Important:</strong><br />This role involves <strong>direct, on-ground sales execution</strong>.<br />It is <strong>not</strong> a digital marketing, content, or office-only position.</p><p>👉 <strong>Apply now</strong> if you’re ready to build real sales skills and fast-track your career through performance.</p>",
